<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Course Pricing Card</title>
<style>
  /* General Reset and Fonts */
  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: transparent; /* Transparent for Wix integration */
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  /* Main Container */
  .container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  /* Header Image Area */
  .header-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
    object-fit: cover;
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Tag on Image */
  .image-tag {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Content Area */
  .content {
    padding: 30px;
  }

  /* Typography */
  h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    color: #111;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: normal;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .price-section {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #111;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .price-detail {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #444;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  /* List Styling */
  .info-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .info-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #333;
  }

  .icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background-color: #ddd; /* Fallback gray circle */
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-right: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  
  /* Icon modifiers */
  .icon.check { background-color: #e0e0e0; color: #555; }
  .icon.medal { background-color: #fceabb; color: #d4af37; font-size: 14px;}
  .icon.star { background-color: #fff4cc; color: #ffbb00; font-size: 14px;}
  .icon.warn { background-color: #ffe6e6; color: #d32f2f; font-size: 14px;}
  .icon.stop { background-color: #ffe6e6; color: #d32f2f; font-size: 14px;}

  /* Second Section (Info Box) */
  .info-box {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    background-color: #fff;
  }

  .info-header {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .info-header h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #222;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  
  .info-header p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  /* Button (Optional based on image blue hint at bottom) */
  .btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #1E90FF;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* Responsive Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .content { padding: 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 18px; }
    .price { font-size: 36px; }
    .info-header h3 { font-size: 24px; }
    .header-image { height: 180px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <!-- 
       IMPORTANT: 
       Since I cannot host the image for you, I have put a placeholder image below.
       You can change the 'src' link below to your own uploaded image URL if you have one.
  -->
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Students" class="header-image">
  
  <div class="content">
    
    <!-- Title Section -->
    <h1>For Iris Liu Only 劉雅芳</h1>
    <h2>多益課程TOEIC -600分/訂閱制/ 2026</h2>

    <!-- Price Section -->
    <div class="price-section">
      <div class="price">NT$ 9,000</div>
      <div class="price-detail">大約20堂課 （每堂50分鐘） 訂閱制</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terms List -->
    <ul class="info-list">
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>預約, 或固定時段上課 （每週固定扣除訂閱制450點）(沒上課也會扣除 450點)</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>週六及國定假日每堂600點</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>🏅 24 小時內提出請假或調課, 扣除0.5堂 (週六/國定假日1堂)</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>🏅 12小時內提出請假或調課, 扣除1堂。(Line 收到時間為主)</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>⭐ 退費：第1~10堂申請，每堂扣除,NT$600後+扣除專案補助費後進行退費。</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>⭐ 退費：第11堂後申請，每堂扣除,NT$550後+扣除專案補助費後，進行退費。</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon warn">!!</span>
        <span>請多加注意, 避免掉入詐騙陷阱！</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon stop">⛔</span>
        <span>此方案為專屬優惠, 請勿與其他人分享！</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="icon check">✓</span>
        <span>此方案無暫停課程選項。</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <!-- Second Card: Class Time Info -->
    <div class="info-box">
      <div class="info-header">
        <h3>上課時間 + 點數須知</h3>
        <p>Tony線上美語家教</p>
      </div>

      <ul class="info-list">
        <li>
          <span class="icon check">✓</span>
          <span>(450)週一～週五 10am~10pm ;週六/國定假日 (600).</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon check">✓</span>
          <span>國定假日需再次確認, 也會提前公告是否有提供上課</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon check">✓</span>
          <span>此方案週六/國定假日若成功預約時段上課, 需600點 （週六學生眾多, 敬請見諒）。（包含國定假日）</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon check">✓</span>
          <span>可以固定時段上課, 非固定時段上課, 請多加利用線上預約系統。</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
